                "data": {
                  "inline": [
                    {
                      "data": {
                        "value": "The neighborhood expressed as an n-D array of 1's and 0's. Default is the n-D square of radius equal to 1 (i.e. a 3x3 square for 2D images, a 3x3x3 cube for 3D images, etc.)"
